ication (M-of-N signatures), hardware enclave provisioning, or specialized compliance reporting?\n          </p>\n          <div className=\"pt-2\">\n            <a \n              href=\"/admin/support\" \n              className=\"inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-1 px-4.5 rounded bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 text-[9.5px] font-bold uppercase text-white border border-white/10 transition-colors\"\n            >\n              <span>Consult Sovereign Architects</span>\n              <ExternalLink className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white/40\" />\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </WorkspaceCard>\n\n      <style dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: `\n        @keyframes glow { \n          0%, 100% { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px rgba(0,255,194,0.2)); } \n          50% { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(0,255,194,0.4)); } \n        }\n        .animate-pulse-glow { animation: glow 2.5s infinite ease-in-out; }\n        .x-icon-offset {\n          transform: translate(11px, 11px) scale(0.9);\n        }\n      `}} />\n\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
