sScanning` state, and the `motion.div` animation. I need to integrate the component with my existing \"Part A\" section, so I'm analyzing how to align the scan progress display with the overall layout, keeping the appearance of the progress bar in mind. I need to assess how scan logs will fit.\n\n\n**Dissecting Workspace Card**\n\nI'm now diving into the details of the WorkspaceCard components, focusing on the Active Sandbox Escapes and System Compliance Score sections. I'm analyzing the structure of these cards, breaking them down into their component parts, and studying their class names to discern their design and layout. I'm paying particular attention to the text sizes, colors, and overall appearance of the numbers and labels. I'm focusing on the relationship between data, visual representation, and the application's overall design.\n\n\n**Evaluating Workspace Card Components**\n\nI'm now deep-diving into the WorkspaceCard components, starting with the System Compliance Score and Hardware Key Sealing sections. I'm focused on text sizes, colors, and the conditional rendering of the HSM status, including the `animate-pulse` class. I'm focusing on the relationship between these elements and the overall visual hierarchy of the card.\n\n\n**Integrating Workspace Card Data**\n\nI'm now integrating new WorkspaceCard components related to continuous tracing. I'm focusing on the visual display of the node count and sync percentage, assessing where this data fits within the existing layout. My focus is on ensuring these additions maintain a clean and informative UI, and how to represent this data effectively.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T08:11:45.647Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"am0vxgze","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/admin/governance/page.tsx","old_text":"      {/* LEFT_CONTENT */}","new_text":"      {/* Toasts */}\n      <div className=\"fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50 flex flex-col gap-2 pointer-events-none select-none\">\n        <AnimatePresence>\n          {toasts.map(t => (\n            <motion.div \n              key={t.id} \n              initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}\n              animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}\n              exit={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.9 }}\n              className={`p-3 rounded-xl shadow-2xl border text-[10px] font-bold flex items-center gap-2 pointer-events-auto max-w-xs ${\n                t.type === \"success\" ? \"bg-black border-[#00FFC2]/30 text-[#00FFC2]\" :\n                t.type === \"warning\" ? \"bg-black border-amber-500/30 text-amber-500\" :\n                \"bg-black border-[#009DFF]/30 text-[#009DFF]\"\n              }`}\n            >\n              {t.type === \"success\" && <CheckCircle className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0\" />}\n              {t.type === \"warning\" && <ShieldAlert className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0\" />}\n              {t.type === \"info\" && <Info className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0\" />}\n              <span>{t.msg}</span>\n            </motion.div>\n          ))}\n        </AnimatePresence>\n      </div>\n\n      <PrivatePageHeader \n        title=\"Oversight & Guardrail Control Desk\" \n        desc=\"System-wide hardware security enclave isolation rules, eBPF telemetry feeds, and real-time sovereign guardrail verification.\"\n        badgeLabel=\"ADMIN SECURITY CONSOLE\"\n      />\n\n      {/* Disclaimer Box */}\n      <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/15 bg-amber-500/[0.02] flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 items-start sm:items-center justify-between\">\n        <div className=\"flex gap-2.5 items-start\">\n          <ShieldAlert className=\"w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n          <div>\n            <span className=\"font-bold uppercase block text-[10px] text-amber-400\">Continuous Enforcement Standard (CES)</span>\n            <span className=\"text-white/60\">Monitors cryptographic sandboxes. Altering policies impacts boundaries instantly.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <button \n          onClick={triggerSystemScan}\n          disabled={isScanning}\n          className=\"h-7.5 px-3 rounded bg-amber-500/10 hover:bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-300 border border-amber-500/20 font-bold uppercase text-[9px] transition-colors flex items-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer disabled:opacity-50 shrink-0\"\n        >\n          {isScanning ? <RefreshCw className=\"w-3 h-3 animate-spin\" /> : <Play className=\"w-3 h-3\" />}\n          {isScanning ? \"Scanning...\" : \"Scan Compliance Matrix\"}\n        </button>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Compliance Scan Drawer */}\n      {isScanning && (\n        <motion.div \n          initial={{ opacity: 0, height: 0 }}\n          animate={{ opacity: 1, height: \"auto\" }}\n          className=\"border border-white/5 bg-black/40 rounded-xl p-3 space-y-2 overflow-hidden\"\n        >\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[9px] text-amber-400\">\n            <span>SECURE LIVE SCAN RUN</span>\n            <span>{scanProgress}% SECURED</span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"w-full bg-white/5 h-1 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n            <div className=\"bg-amber-500 h-full transition-all duration-300\" style={{ width: `${scanProgress}%` }} />\n          </div>\n          <pre className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-h-[100px] overflow-y-auto whitespace-pre-wrap p-2 bg-black/80 rounded border border-white/5 font-mono\">\n            {scanLog}\n          </pre>\n        </motion.div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* Metrics Grid */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"border-[#009DFF]/10\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 uppercase\">Active Sandbox Escapes</div>\n            <div className=\"text-xl font-bold text-white flex items-baseline gap-1.5\">\n              <span>{activeAlertsCount}</span>\n              <span className=\"text-[8px] text-rose-400 px-1 rounded bg-rose-500/10 border border-rose-500/20\">FLAGS</span>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/45 pt-2 border-t border-white/5 mt-2 flex justify-between\">\n              <span>Awaiting review</span>\n              <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">Priority High</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"border-[#00FFC2]/10\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 uppercase\">System Compliance Score</div>\n            <div className=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#00FFC2]\">{overallScore}%</div>\n            <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/45 pt-2 border-t border-white/5 mt-2 flex justify-between\">\n              <span>Active policies</span>\n              <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">{policies.filter(p => p.enforced).length} Rules</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"border-amber-500/10\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 uppercase\">Hardware Key Sealing</div>\n            <div className=\"text-xl font-bold\">\n              <span className={hsmStatus === \"ROTATING\" ? \"text-amber-400 animate-pulse\" : \"text-emerald-400\"}>\n                {hsmStatus === \"ROTATING\" ? `ROTATING...` : hsmStatus === \"ROTATED\" ? \"RE-SEALED\" : \"SEALED\"}\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/45 pt-2 border-t border-white/5 mt-2 flex justify-between items-center\">\n              <span>Dual-signatory HSM</span>\n              <span className=\"text-white/50\">v4.1.8</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"border-white/5\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 uppercase\">Continuous Tracing</div>\n            <div className=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">18 Nodes</div>\n            <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/45 pt-2 border-t border-white/5 mt-2 flex justify-between\">\n              <span>eBPF telemetry pipe</span>\n              <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\">99.998% Sync</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Central Split Grid */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 items-start\">\n        \n        {/* Left Side: Tabs and Main lists */}\n        <div className=\"lg:col-span-2 space-y-4\">\n          {/* TABS_CONTENT */}\n        </div>"}}}
